      "a": "Worth it if international recognition or premium brand recognition matters for your career. JAIN Online BBA at ₹1,35,000 (NAAC A++), Sharda Online BBA at ₹1,20,000 (NAAC A+), and MUJ Online Manipal at ₹1,39,500 are cheaper UGC-DEB approved alternatives. Amity's premium of ₹35,620-₹55,120 over these alternatives is justified for students planning international higher education, working professionals wanting strong domestic brand recognition, family business successors with international ambitions, and students preferring AI-supported learning."
