      "a": "The admission process is fully online: visit amityonline.com, click 'Apply Now', fill in personal and academic details, upload documents (Class 10 and 12 marksheets, passport-size photo, ID proof), pay the application fee of ₹1,100. There is no entrance exam. Admission confirmation is sent via email after document verification. Amity offers two intake sessions per year (January and July) with admission processes typically running 4-6 weeks before each session start."
