      "a": "Most universities accept applicants without work experience, requiring only a bachelor's degree (typically 50% minimum aggregate). However, practical career outcomes are significantly better with prior HR or people-management experience before enrolling. Symbiosis SSODL gives a substantial scholarship to applicants with 2+ years experience. MAHE has a 1-year mandatory work experience requirement."
